The purpose of this blog post is to highlight three potential data sets that our group may focus on for our final project.

## Data Set One: Death rates for suicide by race, age, and Hispanic origin in the United States

This data set was gathered from data.gov, a free database provided by the U.S. Government (https://catalog.data.gov/dataset/death-rates-for-suicide-by-sex-race-hispanic-origin-and-age-united-states-020c1).
